narzedzie-analiz-przestrzennych.przeciecie-opis-funkcjonalnosci: The analysis is based on determining the common part of objects from two different layers. You need to select two layers, the source layer and the intersecting layer, and optionally the objects on these layers for which the common part will be determined. The resulting layer will contain the common part of objects from both layers.
narzedzie-analiz-przestrzennych.zawieranie-nazwa-funkcjonalnosci: Containment of objects within the boundaries of other objects
narzedzie-analiz-przestrzennych.zawieranie-opis-funkcjonalnosci: The analysis is based on determining the objects of the source layer, which are inside the objects of the containing layer. You need to select the source layer from which the objects will be determined and the layer in which they are to be contained. The resulting layer will contain the objects of the source layer that are inside the objects of the containing layer.
narzedzie-analiz-przestrzennych.bufor-nazwa-funkcjonalnosci: Determining the buffer around the objects
narzedzie-analiz-przestrzennych.bufor-opis-funkcjonalnosci: The analysis is based on determining the buffer zone around the objects of the selected layer. You need to select the source layer, optionally the objects on this layer and the size of the buffer - the distance of the buffer zone from the boundaries of the objects. The resulting layer will contain a buffer zone of the specified size around the selected objects.
narzedzie-analiz-przestrzennych.blad-analizy-przestrzennej: No analysis results. Check out selected objects in the analysis.
narzedzie-analiz-przestrzennych.wykonano-analize-komunikat: Spatial analysis was performed. The result layer was added to the map legend.
